      <title>意大利、法国借款人重返德国债务市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/italian-french-borrowers-sweep-back-in-to-german-debt-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国债务市场正在向德国以外的企业重新开放，2024 年筹集融资的法国和意大利借款人数量将超过去年全年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/italian-french-borrowers-sweep-back-in-to-german-debt-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
